# Project Structure

The project follows the standard Next.js App Router structure:

## Core Directories

- `src/app/`: Contains the application pages and API routes
  - `src/app/api/`: API routes using the Next.js API Routes feature
- `public/`: Static assets served at the root path
- `.github/workflows/`: CI/CD pipeline configuration
- `.devcontainer/`: Development container configuration

## Configuration Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project metadata and dependencies
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json): TypeScript compiler options
- [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs): ESLint configuration
- [postcss.config.mjs](mdc:postcss.config.mjs): PostCSS configuration for Tailwind
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts): Next.js configuration
- [Dockerfile](mdc:Dockerfile): Container build instructions
- [.dockerignore](mdc:.dockerignore): Files to exclude from Docker builds
